Type: Package
Package: tidySpatialExperiment
Title: Brings SpatialExperiment to the Tidyverse 
Version: 1.9.4
Authors@R: c(person("Stefano", "Mangiola", email = "mangiolastefano@gmail.com",
                  role = c("aut", "cre")) )
Description: tidySpatialExperiment is an adapter that abstracts the 'SpatialExperiment' container 
    in the form of a tibble and allows the data manipulation, plotting and nesting using 'tidyverse'.
License: GPL-3
